21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_tkey(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24 dns_rcode_t rcode;
25 dns_name_t name;
26 isc_buffer_t buffer;
27 long i;
28 char *e;
29
30 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_tkey);
31
32 UNUSED(type);
33 UNUSED(rdclass);
34 UNUSED(callbacks);
35
36 /*
37 * Algorithm.
38 */
39 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
40 false));
41 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
42 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
43 if (origin == NULL)
44 origin = dns_rootname;
45 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options, target));
46
47
48 /*
49 * Inception.
50 */
51 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
52 false));
53 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
54
55 /*
56 * Expiration.
57 */
58 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
59 false));
60 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
61
62 /*
63 * Mode.
64 */
65 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
66 false));
67 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
68 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
69 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
70
71 /*
72 * Error.
73 */
74 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
75 false));
76 if (dns_tsigrcode_fromtext(&rcode, &token.value.as_textregion)
77 != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
78 {
79 i = strtol(DNS_AS_STR(token), &e, 10);
80 if (*e != 0)
81 RETTOK(DNS_R_UNKNOWN);
82 if (i < 0 || i > 0xffff)
83 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
84 rcode = (dns_rcode_t)i;
85 }
86 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(rcode, target));
87
88 /*
89 * Key Size.
90 */
91 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
92 false));
93 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
94 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
95 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
96
97 /*
98 * Key Data.
99 */
100 RETERR(isc_base64_tobuffer(lexer, target, (int)token.value.as_ulong));
101
102 /*
103 * Other Size.
104 */
105 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
106 false));
107 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
108 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
109 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
110
111 /*
112 * Other Data.
113 */
114 return (isc_base64_tobuffer(lexer, target, (int)token.value.as_ulong));
115}

117static inline isc_result_t
118totext_tkey(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
119 isc_region_t sr, dr;
120 char buf[sizeof("4294967295 ")];
121 unsigned long n;
122 dns_name_t name;
123 dns_name_t prefix;
124 bool sub;
125
126 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_tkey);
127 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
128
129 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
130
131 /*
132 * Algorithm.
133 */
134 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
135 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
136 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &sr);
137 sub = name_prefix(&name, tctx->origin, &prefix);
138 RETERR(dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
139 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
140 isc_region_consume(&sr, name_length(&name));
141
142 /*
143 * Inception.
144 */
145 n = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
146 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
147 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%lu ", n);
148 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
149
150 /*
151 * Expiration.
152 */
153 n = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
154 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
155 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%lu ", n);
156 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
157
158 /*
159 * Mode.
160 */
161 n = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
162 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
163 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%lu ", n);
164 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
165
166 /*
167 * Error.
168 */
169 n = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
170 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
171 if (dns_tsigrcode_totext((dns_rcode_t)n, target) == ISC_R_SUCCESS)
172 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
173 else {
174 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%lu ", n);
175 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
176 }
177
178 /*
179 * Key Size.
180 */
181 n = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
182 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
183 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%lu", n);
184 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
185
186 /*
187 * Key Data.
188 */
189 REQUIRE(n <= sr.length);
190 dr = sr;
191 dr.length = n;
192 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
193 RETERR(str_totext(" (", target));
194 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
195 if (tctx->width == 0) /* No splitting */
196 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&dr, 60, "", target));
197 else
198 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&dr, tctx->width - 2,
199 tctx->linebreak, target));
200 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
201 RETERR(str_totext(" ) ", target));
202 else
203 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
204 isc_region_consume(&sr, n);
205
206 /*
207 * Other Size.
208 */
209 n = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
210 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
211 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%lu", n);
212 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
213
214 /*
215 * Other Data.
216 */
217 REQUIRE(n <= sr.length);
218 if (n != 0U) {
219 dr = sr;
220 dr.length = n;
221 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
222 RETERR(str_totext(" (", target));
223 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
224 if (tctx->width == 0) /* No splitting */
225 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&dr, 60, "", target));
226 else
227 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&dr, tctx->width - 2,
228 tctx->linebreak, target));
229 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
230 RETERR(str_totext(" )", target));
231 }
232 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
233}

235static inline isc_result_t
236fromwire_tkey(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
237 isc_region_t sr;
238 unsigned long n;
239 dns_name_t name;
240
241 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_tkey);
242
243 UNUSED(type);
244 UNUSED(rdclass);
245
246 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
247
248 /*
249 * Algorithm.
250 */
251 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
252 RETERR(dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
253
254 /*
255 * Inception: 4
256 * Expiration: 4
257 * Mode: 2
258 * Error: 2
259 */
260 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
261 if (sr.length < 12)
262 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
263 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, 12));
264 isc_region_consume(&sr, 12);
265 isc_buffer_forward(source, 12);
266
267 /*
268 * Key Length + Key Data.
269 */
270 if (sr.length < 2)
271 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
272 n = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
273 if (sr.length < n + 2)
274 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
275 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, n + 2));
276 isc_region_consume(&sr, n + 2);
277 isc_buffer_forward(source, n + 2);
278
279 /*
280 * Other Length + Other Data.
281 */
282 if (sr.length < 2)
283 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
284 n = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
285 if (sr.length < n + 2)
286 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
287 isc_buffer_forward(source, n + 2);
288 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, n + 2));
289}

291static inline isc_result_t
292towire_tkey(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
293 isc_region_t sr;
294 dns_name_t name;
295 dns_offsets_t offsets;
296
297 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_tkey);
298 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
299
300 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
301 /*
302 * Algorithm.
303 */
304 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
305 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
306 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &sr);
307 RETERR(dns_name_towire(&name, cctx, target));
308 isc_region_consume(&sr, name_length(&name));
309
310 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
311}

313static inline int
314compare_tkey(ARGS_COMPARE) {
315 isc_region_t r1;
316 isc_region_t r2;
317 dns_name_t name1;
318 dns_name_t name2;
319 int order;
320
321 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
322 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
323 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_tkey);
324 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
325 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
326
327 /*
328 * Algorithm.
329 */
330 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
331 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
332 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
333 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
334 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &r1);
335 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &r2);
336 if ((order = dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2)) != 0)
337 return (order);
338 isc_region_consume(&r1, name_length(&name1));
339 isc_region_consume(&r2, name_length(&name2));
340 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
341}

343static inline isc_result_t
344fromstruct_tkey(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
345 dns_rdata_tkey_t *tkey = source;
346
347 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_tkey);
348 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
349 REQUIRE(tkey->common.rdtype == type);
350 REQUIRE(tkey->common.rdclass == rdclass);
351
352 UNUSED(type);
353 UNUSED(rdclass);
354
355 /*
356 * Algorithm Name.
357 */
358 RETERR(name_tobuffer(&tkey->algorithm, target));
359
360 /*
361 * Inception: 32 bits.
362 */
363 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(tkey->inception, target));
364
365 /*
366 * Expire: 32 bits.
367 */
368 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(tkey->expire, target));
369
370 /*
371 * Mode: 16 bits.
372 */
373 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(tkey->mode, target));
374
375 /*
376 * Error: 16 bits.
377 */
378 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(tkey->error, target));
379
380 /*
381 * Key size: 16 bits.
382 */
383 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(tkey->keylen, target));
384
385 /*
386 * Key.
387 */
388 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, tkey->key, tkey->keylen));
389
390 /*
391 * Other size: 16 bits.
392 */
393 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(tkey->otherlen, target));
394
395 /*
396 * Other data.
397 */
398 return (mem_tobuffer(target, tkey->other, tkey->otherlen));
399}

401static inline isc_result_t
402tostruct_tkey(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
403 dns_rdata_tkey_t *tkey = target;
404 dns_name_t alg;
405 isc_region_t sr;
406
407 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_tkey);
408 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
409 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
410
411 tkey->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
412 tkey->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
413 ISC_LINK_INIT(&tkey->common, link);
414
415 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
416
417 /*
418 * Algorithm Name.
419 */
420 dns_name_init(&alg, NULL);
421 dns_name_fromregion(&alg, &sr);
422 dns_name_init(&tkey->algorithm, NULL);
423 RETERR(name_duporclone(&alg, mctx, &tkey->algorithm));
424 isc_region_consume(&sr, name_length(&tkey->algorithm));
425
426 /*
427 * Inception.
428 */
429 tkey->inception = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
430 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
431
432 /*
433 * Expire.
434 */
435 tkey->expire = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
436 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
437
438 /*
439 * Mode.
440 */
441 tkey->mode = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
442 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
443
444 /*
445 * Error.
446 */
447 tkey->error = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
448 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
449
450 /*
451 * Key size.
452 */
453 tkey->keylen = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
454 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
455
456 /*
457 * Key.
458 */
459 INSIST(tkey->keylen + 2U <= sr.length);
460 tkey->key = mem_maybedup(mctx, sr.base, tkey->keylen);
461 if (tkey->key == NULL)
462 goto cleanup;
463 isc_region_consume(&sr, tkey->keylen);
464
465 /*
466 * Other size.
467 */
468 tkey->otherlen = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
469 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
470
471 /*
472 * Other.
473 */
474 INSIST(tkey->otherlen <= sr.length);
475 tkey->other = mem_maybedup(mctx, sr.base, tkey->otherlen);
476 if (tkey->other == NULL)
477 goto cleanup;
478
479 tkey->mctx = mctx;
480 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
481
482 cleanup:
483 if (mctx != NULL)
484 dns_name_free(&tkey->algorithm, mctx);
485 if (mctx != NULL && tkey->key != NULL)
486 isc_mem_free(mctx, tkey->key);
487 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
488}
489
490static inline void
491freestruct_tkey(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
492 dns_rdata_tkey_t *tkey = (dns_rdata_tkey_t *) source;
493
494 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
495
496 if (tkey->mctx == NULL)
497 return;
498
499 dns_name_free(&tkey->algorithm, tkey->mctx);
500 if (tkey->key != NULL)
501 isc_mem_free(tkey->mctx, tkey->key);
502 if (tkey->other != NULL)
503 isc_mem_free(tkey->mctx, tkey->other);
504 tkey->mctx = NULL;
505}
